    <ownedClass>
        <class isAbstract="false" name="Author">
            <derivationSupplier className="Participation" staticModelDerivationId="1"/>
            <graphicRepresentation presentation="HL7">
                <graphElement containerDiagramName="Main"
                    nodeOrientation="Left" shapeId="Sheet.23"
                    shapeTemplate="Participation" textWrappingWidth="66.0">
                    <position x="2.23153" y="4.33346"/>
                    <size height="0.56944" width="3.48032"/>
                </graphElement>
            </graphicRepresentation>
            <annotations>
                <designComments>
                    <text>
                        <p>Author includes publishing time of the report.</p>
                        <p>Messaging time of the report is not carried in payload, only in wrappers.</p>
                    </text>
                    <graphicRepresentation>
                        <graphElement containerDiagramName="Main"
                            isHeightAutoSize="true"
                            isWidthAutoSize="false" shapeId="Sheet.268">
                            <position x="6.02925" y="4.73833"/>
                            <size height="0.85556" width="1.725"/>
                            <anchorage connectToShapeId="Sheet.23">
                                <position x="6.89175" y="5.16611"/>
                                <graphEdge>
                                    <anchor>
                                    <position x="4.03121" y="4.90291"/>
                                    </anchor>
                                </graphEdge>
                            </anchorage>
                        </graphElement>
                    </graphicRepresentation>
                </designComments>
                <otherAnnotation type="html">
                    <text>
                        <P>The Author of a Laboratory report may be filled by the department responsible for the report, the person representing the department or the actual author of the report. In many cases, the department will be used unless there is a reason for identification of a specific person as may occur with Histopathology reporting.</P>
                        <P>
                            <B>Refers to the person or department responsible for authorising the laboratory report. In most cases, this will be the department in which the work was performed. In some instances, e.g. Histopathology reports, there may be a requirement to identify the actual person authoring the report.</B>
                        </P>
                    </text>
                </otherAnnotation>
            </annotations>
            <attribute conformance="R" fixedValue="AUT"
                isMandatory="true" isStructural="true"
                maximumMultiplicity="1" minimumMultiplicity="1"
                name="typeCode" sortKey="5">
                <annotations>
                    <otherAnnotation type="html">
                        <text>
                            <p>Indicates that the role is the author of the report.</p>
                        </text>
                    </otherAnnotation>
                </annotations>
                <derivationSupplier attributeName="typeCode"
                    className="Participation" staticModelDerivationId="1"/>
                <type name="CS"/>
                <supplierDomainSpecification codingStrength="CNE" domainName="AUT"/>
            </attribute>
            <attribute conformance="R" defaultValue="OP"
                isMandatory="true" isStructural="true"
                maximumMultiplicity="1" minimumMultiplicity="1"
                name="contextControlCode" sortKey="7">
                <annotations>
                    <otherAnnotation type="html">
                        <text>
                            <P>A code that specifies how this Participation contributes to the context of the current Act and whether it may be propagated to descendant Acts whose association allows such propagation.</P>
                        </text>
                    </otherAnnotation>
                </annotations>
                <derivationSupplier attributeName="contextControlCode"
                    className="Participation" staticModelDerivationId="1"/>
                <type name="CS"/>
                <supplierDomainSpecification codingStrength="CNE" domainName="ContextControl"/>
            </attribute>
            <attribute conformance="R" isMandatory="true"
                maximumMultiplicity="1" minimumMultiplicity="1"
                name="time" sortKey="11">
                <annotations>
                    <otherAnnotation type="html">
                        <text>
